Package: SAVA
Type: Package
Title: Safe, Always-Valid Alpha-Investing Rules For Doubly Sequential Online Inference
Version: 1.0
Date: 2026-06-22
Author: Zeyu Yao, Bowen Gang, Wenguang Sun
Maintainer: Questions and comments to <bgang@fudan.edu.cn>
Description: Implements the Safe Always-Valid Alpha-Investing (SAVA) procedures proposed in the paper ``Safe, Always-Valid Alpha-Investing Rules for Doubly Sequential Online Inference''. The package contains functions used in the simulation studies and data analyses reported in the manuscript.
